Task One Psuedocode

1. Generate 2 random numbers less than 100
2. Store first number in variable number1
3. Store second number in variable number2
4. Prompt the user to give an answer to the sum of number1 and number2
5. Collect user input
6. Store as user_answer
7a. If user_answer only consists of digits, cast it as an int
   i. Display result of the expression user_answer == number1 + number2
b. Else, display "False"